spells.description:
Equip: Your melee attacks have a chance to putt a bomb toward your enemy, dealing 159,524 Fire damage on impact.

When you exit combat, gain a burst of speed for 10 sec if your score is a Hole-in-One, Birdie, or Par.

Use: Fashion nearby garbage into a sphere and launch it into the sky. After 3 sec of gathering momentum the sphere crashes into the targeted location dealing 1.7 million Physical damage split between all enemies in the area. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Gain a high chance to follow up your attacks with a fiery gilded uppercut, dealing 372,319 Fire damage to your target. Molten gold continues to splatter to deal 103,422 Fire damage over 5 sec to all nearby enemies. Damage reduced beyond 8 enemies.
